    <item>
      <title>Fix lock-closed-issues workflow: use search API instead of offset pagination (#69470)</title>
      <link>https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/commit/baf38ddaaa030ce9a7a63acde82ca95e90cd95f6</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">baf38dd</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 00:15:49 GMT</pubDate>
      <category>gh-commits-claude-code</category>
      <description>The workflow has been failing daily since 2026-04-27 with HTTP 422 &quot;Pagination with the page parameter is not supported for large datasets&quot; at page=100. The repo now has ~58k closed issues and the script was paging past ~10k already-locked ones every run before reaching any candidates.  Replace list</description>
